    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. This example excels in driving dynamics, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a serviced double-VANOS system to ensure long-term structural and valvetrain integrity. The suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein dampers for improved rebound control, while the factory limited-slip differential provides excellent traction out of corners. Though the finish shows minor road-induced patina, the engine pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline with a linear power band. Recent fluid analysis and a cooling system overhaul make this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning driver.",
